2023-10-23  Nathan Potter  <ndp@opendap.org>

	Vls scalar (#833)
	* Added a solution for the Variable Length String
	Scalar case. This solution reads the string
	during dmr++ creation, converts the DAP variable
	to a compact representation, and then stores the
	value in the compact variable so that the runtime
	code need not read it from the remote data object.
	* Comments and a new test for VLSS
	* Fixing get_drmpp inventory test. Probably needs a review

2023-10-23  myang6  <myang6@hdfgroup.org>

