2023-06-05  James Gallagher  <jgallagher@opendap.org>
	    Florian Weimer  <fweimer@redhat.com>

	modules/hdf5_handler/gctp: C99 compatibility improvements (#775)
	* modules/hdf5_handler/gctp: C99 compatibility improvements
	This change adds additional prototypes to avoid implicit
	function declarations, which will not be supported by future
	compilers by default, resulting in build failures.  Also add a
	missing int type, which future compilers will require, too.
	The additional prototypes revealed that the wrapper function gctp_
	has the wrong signature, which is also fixed in this commit.
	Update gctp_prototypes.h
	Update br_gctp.c
	Update gctp.c
	---------

