2023-05-15  Nathan Potter  <ndp@opendap.org>

	Fixing get_dmrpp baselines - chunk offset changes (#769)

2023-05-11  James Gallagher  <jgallagher@opendap.org>

	RemoteResource retry fix (#771)
	* Fixed the RemoteResources retry code
	The problem was that ftruncate was used to remove an error
	message from the file used to hold the response as it was
	read from the network. However, the file descriptor was not
	rewound to the start of the file, so the valid response data
	was written starting past the initial position. A reader would see the
	initial part of the temporary file as filled with nulls. This
	error was introduced with RR was rewritten.
	Also refactored the CmrApiTest.cc code since this work overlapped
	the CMR legacy API and I was working on those tests.
	Added tests for the RR retry fix

2023-05-11  Nathan Potter  <ndp@opendap.org>

	Fixing production rules so that netcdf is linked with libxml2 (#770)
	* Fixing production rules so that netcdf is linked with libxml2
	* Adding libxml2 to dispatch/unit-tests build
	* Using XML2_LIBS variable

2023-05-08  James Gallagher  <jgallagher@opendap.org>

	Cutil refactor 04.26.23 (#766)

	Undo the CMR API test patch
	The legacy API stopped working for a while, returning 404, now
	it works again.

