	If we decide that the coverage for the non-hdf modules is needed,
	then let's make a new set of 'check targets' in the bes/modules
	Makefile.am so that 'make check' can be more targeted and lets
	also make a fourth scan process to even out the load.

2023-04-20  James Gallagher  <jgallagher@opendap.org>

	Changes that filter the effective URL to remove credentials (#758)
	In some cases, security tokens (which in NGAP can last for months)
	were leaked to log files and error messages. This branch filters
	the URLs that contain those credentials, leaving most of the URL
	but removing the 'security parts.'
	Bonus: The RemoteResource HTTP fetch is now timed.

