	Frankenbranch (#752)
	The Build DMR++ module and the RemoteResource changes.
	This merge includes the additions for the Build DMR++ module of the BES
	and the changes to the bes/http convenience library that removes caching
	from the RemoteResource class. Other changes include the way RR is used
	in various modules in the BES, including the NGAP, Gateway, and HTTP
	catalog modules.

