2023-02-03  James Gallagher  <jgallagher@opendap.org>

	Bes keys fix (#733)
	TheBESKeys --> unique_ptr pattern
	* TheBESKeys now uses a unique_ptr and passes tests.
	Some other code had to be changed because the singleton
	was 'messed with' by some of the BES framework destructors
	and some of the unit-tests. I added a reload_keys() method
	to enable unit-tests to switch key files and/or reload the
	original key file, effectively resetting changes they might
	have made during the tests.

