2023-02-01  James Gallagher  <jgallagher@opendap.org>

	Use C++14 for the builds by default (#731)
	Use C++14 for the builds by default
	* Also removed the OSX_Resources stuff.
	* Various fixes to configure and friends to minimize autoreconf errors.
	* Drop the autoconf version to 2.69 from 2.71.
	* The h5common.cc/h files in modules/dmrpp_handler are now 'built sources.'
	This preserves the SSOT for these files as the modules/hdf5_handler
	directory. The files are 'built' by copying them into the modules/
	dmrpp_module so they can be used by the build_dmrpp code.
	Made a new 'common' library for testing code; migrated as much as possible

