2022-11-07  James Gallagher  <jgallagher@opendap.org>

	Reformatting only (#698)

	Typo in configure.ac
	[skip ci]

	S3 signing (#695)
	Added S3 URL signing when there are credentials
	If the BES is configured with credentials for a given
	URL (via conf file or env vars), they will be used to
	sign a URL that matches those credentials.
	Also added credentials.conf to gitignore
	Added a test for S3 URL signing - works

