	Added filter to errors written to log. Internal, InternalFatal, and Forbidden errors are always written to the log. SyntaxUseer and Not Found errors are only writtent when the log is set to verbose mode.

	Added filter to errors written to log. Internal, InternalFatal, and Forbidden errors are always written to the log. SyntaxUseer and Not Found errors are only writtent when the log is set to verbose mode.

